				<wikidot:authorName>Deadcanons</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2821677</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It took a little while to grow on me, but once it did, it REALLY grew on me. Good work. I loved the use of 2521 especially; good match-up of anomalies, and I love how &quot;carefully&quot; you worded the incident description.</p> <p>The ending is&#8230; a bit of a big cheese pill, don't you think? But I like the rest of it enough to upvote anyway.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
